The President of Black First Land First (BLF), Comrade Andile Mngxitama, shall on “freedom day” address the nation under the title “Freedom is Land”. The address shall amongst others respond to the biggest scam going on in parliament under the name of Land Expropriation Without Compensation. BLF will explain why land is central to our liberation and also update the nation on the struggle around the Sodwana Bay Lodge. BLF shall further respond to the ongoing murders of blacks on farms, Tito Mboweni’s lies and the demonization of Tokyo Sexwale. The address will in addition clarify why BLF says the Cuban engineers must go home! Tune in to the LIVE broadcast on Black First Land First Facebook page at 12:00,on 27 April 2021. Issued by Black First Land First, National Coordinating Committee (BLF NCC)
26 April 2021 Contact Details Black First Land First Mail: blackfirstlandfirst@gmail.com
